                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130602-79-off417 t18130602-79-cd418"></join>, twenty-eight yards of printed cotton, value 2 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18130602-79-victim764" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Gunn
                  <interp inst="t18130602-79-victim764" type="surname" value="Gunn"></interp>
